```plantuml
@startuml gdsc-ys_mlops

actor ML_Developer
participant "Client-Side Tools" as Client
participant "Nginx Reverse Proxy" as Nginx
participant "MLflow Tracking Server" as MLflow
participant "MySQL Database" as MySQL
participant "AWS S3" as S3

ML_Developer -> Client: Initiate Experiment Tracking
Client -> MLflow: Log Experiment Details
MLflow -> MySQL: Store Metadata
MLflow -> S3: Upload Artifacts

ML_Developer -> Client: Request Experiment Data
Client -> Nginx: HTTP Request
Nginx -> MLflow: Forward Request
MLflow -> MySQL: Fetch Metadata
MLflow -> S3: Retrieve Artifacts
MLflow -> Nginx: Send Experiment Data
Nginx -> Client: Forward Response

ML_Developer -> Client: Deploy Model
Client -> MLflow: Build Docker Image
MLflow -> S3: Fetch Model Artifacts
MLflow -> Docker: Build Container Image

ML_Developer -> Client: Query Model Registry
Client -> MLflow: REST API Call
MLflow -> MySQL: Retrieve Model Information

@enduml
```